snippet: Tiger Woods struggled through back pain during the second round of the P.G.A. Championship and missed the cut for only the fourth time in 66 major championships as a professional.
abstract: Tiger Woods shoots 74 in second round of PGA Championship and misses the cut for only the fourth time in 66 major championships as a professional.
